    {
        "Id": 97,
        "ActionId": 97,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The Chief Technician lets out a sigh.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 98,
        "ActionId": 98,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'I\\'ll send you a detailed report later, but put simply, Amalgamation technology is a bridge connecting individual M.I.N.D.s. Its ultimate objective is to construct a vast consciousness network: the Amalgamation array.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 99,
        "ActionId": 99,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '12'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 100,
        "ActionId": 100,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Mina', 3: 'I saw that much firsthand. Everyone linked gets a massive power boost... even starts using tech they shouldn\\'t understand.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 101,
        "ActionId": 101,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'It\\'s not just enhancement. It is completion. We previously misidentified the instability in the Arctic Route Union\\'s humanoid-hybrid M.I.N.D.s as a flaw. In reality, it was a deliberate design gap.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 102,
        "ActionId": 102,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '4'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 103,
        "ActionId": 103,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Mina', 3: 'Are you saying they engineered humanoid-hybrids specifically for Amalgamation?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 104,
        "ActionId": 104,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Correct. Bionic machines possess dedicated Amalgamation access points. Non-humanoid collectives induce M.I.N.D. instability, but these perceived defects perfectly complement Amalgamation\\'s requirements.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 105,
        "ActionId": 105,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'The technology\\'s purpose is to construct a macro-array from countless individual nodes, recalibrating each unique entity—from individual to collective, and back again.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 106,
        "ActionId": 106,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Mina', 3: 'So after the Amalgamation, they become \"complete\"... That explains the historical obsession with perfecting humanoid-hybrid frames.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 107,
        "ActionId": 107,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 306,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 108,
        "ActionId": 108,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '3'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 109,
        "ActionId": 109,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: '\"Ultimate Amalgamator Malkuth\"—a term Mina recalls from the manuscript during her talk with Asimov. This, she now understands, is the key. \"Complete\" doesn\\'t just mean the Amalgamator is finished; it means the entire system, including its subordinate frames, is now whole.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 110,
        "ActionId": 110,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 306,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '0'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 111,
        "ActionId": 111,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '4'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 112,
        "ActionId": 112,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Shared consciousness, mutual reinforcement—that is the true purpose of Amalgamation\\'s power. A communal existence defines Malkuth\\'s core strength.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 113,
        "ActionId": 113,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Mina', 3: 'But if that\\'s the ideal... what\\'s with the red aurora? What kind of Amalgamation is the Frostheart Emperor running?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 114,
        "ActionId": 114,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'A corrupted variant.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 115,
        "ActionId": 115,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Similar to Amberia\\'s prior misuse, while she employed the power of Amalgamation, her core methodology was appropriation, subsuming other nodes within the array as mere extensions of her own will.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 116,
        "ActionId": 116,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Mina', 3: 'But wouldn\\'t that break the proper connection between the Amalgamator, the humanoid-hybrids, and the bionic machines?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 117,
        "ActionId": 117,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Connection is not the requirement. He only needs to activate the combat modules.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 118,
        "ActionId": 118,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Immersion in anger teaches hatred, a principle applicable to any thinking entity. Complex consciousness synchronization is unnecessary. Implanting a single, dominant emotion or command suffices.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 119,
        "ActionId": 119,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '12'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 120,
        "ActionId": 120,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Mina', 3: 'No synchronization needed... Wait, so he doesn\\'t need an anchor like Derek in our case...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 121,
        "ActionId": 121,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Indeed. I suspect our initial activation failure was within his anticipated parameters.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 122,
        "ActionId": 122,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '4'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 123,
        "ActionId": 123,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Mina', 3: 'Hmph. Too bad for him we got it working in the end... Speaking of which, what exactly did you connect to handle the processing load?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 124,
        "ActionId": 124,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'A large-scale server cluster, provided by an associate who operates under the designation \"The Unwinged\".', 4: '2'}"
    },
